A selection of layered synth patterns that will provide the building blocks for creating up-tempo Dance, Trance and Techno tracks. With sweeping filters and arpeggiated riffs, the loops in this pack will inject movement into your compositions.
FEATURES:
- 40 Dance / Trance Synth Loops in WAV format;
- 37 Dance / Trance Synth Loops in REX2 format;
- BPM range: 120-140 BPM;
- All loops are 44KHz/16bit WAV and REX2, these formats are compatible with all audio applications;
- All Royalty Free.

